rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0001
rows.name: According to Shiki, it says...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0002
rows.name:
"'Something Park Parking Lot...' a-and,
'I can't read the rest.'"

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0003
rows.name: ...is what she said, apparently.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0004
rows.name: So this hill used to be a park, huh?

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0101
rows.name: According to Shiki...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0102
rows.name:
"It says 'Something Park Parking Lot...'
and then 'I can't read the rest.'"

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0103
rows.name: ...That's what she said, anyway.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0104
rows.name: So this place used to be a park...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0201
rows.name: I had Shiki read it, and...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0202
rows.name:
"It seems to say 'Something Park
Parking Lot...' and 'I can't read the rest...'"

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0203
rows.name: ...is what she said, mo.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0204
rows.name: So that means this hill was a park, mo.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0301
rows.name: I had Shiki decipher it.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0302
rows.name:
It appears to say, "'Something Park
Parking Lot...'"

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0303
rows.name: So be it.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0304
rows.name:
So the hill that Rex saw in his dream
was once a park...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0401
rows.name: According to Shiki...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0402
rows.name:
She said, "'Something Park Parking Lot...'
'and I can't read the rest.'"

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0403
rows.name: ...is what she claimed.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0404
rows.name:
If we polished this sign up a bit,
maybe she'd be able to read more of it.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0501
rows.name:
This must be a sign of some kind,
but I can't read it at all.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0601
rows.name: I can't read what's written here at all.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0701
rows.name:
Something's written on this paper-thin
board, but I can't read it, mo...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0801
rows.name:
This panel is so thin... and yet
it is remarkably sturdy. Such
masterful technology.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0901
rows.name:
This probably explains something
about this place, but I can't read a lick of it.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0902
rows.name: (When examined by Rex)

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1001
rows.name: So this... is Eden?

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1002
rows.name:
No... Standing here thinking about it
won't help. Let's move on.

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0904
rows.name: (When examined by Nia)

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1101
rows.name: This is Eden...?

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1102
rows.name: It looks a lot like the Land of Mors...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0906
rows.name: (When examined by Tora)

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1201
rows.name:
What a lonely place, mo...
Is a place like this really Eden, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1202
rows.name:
The technology looks incredible, but it
doesn't seem like a place people can live, mo...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0908
rows.name: (When examined by Meleph)

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1301
rows.name: So this is Eden?

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1302
rows.name: It is a land more barren than even Superbia...

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg0910
rows.name: (When examined by Zeke)

rows.label: tlk00000591_01_msg1401
rows.name:
We finally made it all this way...
To think this is the sight that was waiting for us.
